          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unblock <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr" >@<b>SafetyPinDaily</b></span></button>

  <style>
    /* Global svg style overrides the overflow. Added svg for specificity */
    svg.RadialCounter {
      margin-bottom: -4px;
      overflow: visible;
      transform: rotate(-90deg);
    }

    .RadialCounter--safe {
      stroke: #1da1f2;

      stroke: #ccd6dd;
    }

    @keyframes RadialCounterPulse {
      0% { stroke-width:2 }
      50% { stroke-width: 4; }
      100% { stroke-width: 2; }
    }

    .RadialCounter--danger.RadialCounter--pulse,
    .RadialCounter--warn.RadialCounter--pulse {
      animation: RadialCounterPulse 0.3s ease-in-out;
      animation-iteration-count: 1;
    }
  </style>
  <circle class="RadialCounter-progressUnderlay" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="8" fill="none" stroke-width="1" />
  <circle class="js-progress-circle" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="8" fill="none" stroke-width="2">
  </circle>
</svg>
